        "description": {
            "value": "<p>This <em>+2 greater striking cunning wounding sawtooth</em> saber appears rusty but never loses its edge. It's drawn to the blood of your targets. You gain a +2 item bonus to [[/act seek]] or [[/act track]] creatures that have blood.</p>\n<p><strong>Activate—Call of the Bloodthirst</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">r</span></p>\n<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per hour</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within 60 feet takes bleed damage</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> You cast translocate, appearing adjacent to the triggering creature, then Strike it with this weapon. The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] to the attack.</p>"
